Project Info

Description:

Tic-Tac-Toe app built with React.

Features three game modes:
  • Same-screen multiplayer
  • Real-time online multiplayer
  • Singleplayer vs. "AI" (not really AI)

Front-End:

  • React
  • Sass

Back-End:

  • Node.js
  • Next.js
  • Express
  • Socket.IO

Build/Deploy:

  • Docker

Hosting:

  • Google Cloud Run
